Text: Hai..i'm sunny from indonesia.My uncle also stay in indonesia.One time i go
  to the bali that time they people celebrate day of silence and shock.How to baliness
  celebrate day of silence(nyepi).They people are amazing how strong baliness for
  relegion.That day no light no internet and no veheicle on the road.I like so much
  in my life only that day i feel relax.So amazing experince for me.Nowadays i stay
  in jakarta and i wish to go there during day of silence.I love bali.
